OL,3,CMan in hospital after car
OL,4,C'deliberately' driven into him
OL,6,FA man is in hospital after a car was
OL,7,F"deliberately" driven into him.JThe
OL,8,Fincident happened yesterday, 15 May,
OL,9,Fjust after 6pm on Berkley Street,
OL,10,Fclose to the junction with Upper
OL,11,FStanhope Street in Toxteth, Liverpool.
OL,13,FPolice confirmed a 31-year old man was
OL,14,Fhit by a grey Mercedes GLA. After
OL,15,Frunning the man over, three men got
OL,16,Fout of the car and assaulted him.JThe
OL,17,FMercedes was then driven off down
OL,18,FEmerson Street. It was found a short
OL,19,Ftime later on Cairns Street and seized
OL,20,Fby police for forensic examination.
