OL,6,FThe victim was treated by paramedics
OL,7,Fat the scene and taken to hospital for
OL,8,Ftreatment for cuts to the head and a
OL,9,Fleg injury. His condition is described
OL,10,Fas stable.
OL,12,FMerseyside Police are appealing for
OL,13,Fany witnesses, CCTV and dash camera
OL,14,Ffootage which may assist their
OL,15,Finvestigation.JDetective Inspector
OL,16,FDarren Taylor of Merseyside Police
OL,17,Fsaid: "Our investigation into this
OL,18,Fincident is in its very early stages,
OL,19,Fbut it does appear the car was
OL,20,Fdeliberately driven at the man who was
OL,21,Fthen assaulted by the occupants.
