OL,3,CMan in hospital after car
OL,4,C'deliberately' driven into him
OL,6,F"Not only would this have been a
OL,7,Ftraumatic experience for the victim,
OL,8,Fbut it would have been shocking for
OL,9,Fany onlookers.
OL,11,F"We have launched an investigation
OL,12,Finto what happened and have already
OL,13,Fseized the car we believe was
OL,14,Finvolved. Our officers are continuing
OL,15,Fto undertake an extensive search of
OL,16,Fthe area and studying CCTV footage to
OL,17,Festablish the full circumstances and
OL,18,Flocate the offenders.
