OL,3,CMan in hospital after car
OL,4,C'deliberately' driven into him
OL,6,F"I appeal to anyone who witnessed this
OL,7,Fincident, and any residents living
OL,8,Flocally who might have CCTV of a
OL,9,Fvehicle in the area between 6-6.45pm
OL,10,Fto please contact us. Alternatively,
OL,11,Fif you were driving in the vicinity I
OL,12,Fask that you please check your dashcam
OL,13,Ffootage that may have captured the
OL,14,Fincident or the car and to also come
OL,15,Fforward.J"Every piece of information
OL,16,Fis vitally important to our
OL,17,Finvestigation and could help us
OL,18,Festablish what happened so we can
OL,19,Fprovide answers for his family."
